{"type": "article", "id": 13316, "title": "迷你耳机放大器", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-11T06:50:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606004259UVvYM0ojxLCZWspu.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>AQUA 是 Nexum 推出的一款迷你耳机放大器，相对市面上的耳机放大器，它小巧轻便，极其便于携带。AQUA有一个内置的电源，不需要任何电源接口。同时，它可以与各种款式的耳机兼容，并能够将任何形式的音乐文件转换成 MP3 格式，适用于 iOS 和 Android 系统。目前产品在 Kickstaeter 上众筹，预计今年 11 月份发售。</span><a href=\"http://www.molu-aqua.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a><span>可以查看详细信息。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004255c90PrmFdgSYIaQst.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57579462\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606060042560ozGfSHl4LqyKbwJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57701711\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004257b5us3hXcozlMiEQZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57701711\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004257MfV4aDbR0v7yn5gO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004257iv0y3FtarDBpsGL5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56601467\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606004258IDXsc5eMYx2wtjWQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57090465\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}